Genitalia
♂: lateral process of gonostyli digitiform, rounded apically, placed at basal third of height in lateral view (fig. 
29
), placed laterally in ventral view; gonostyli in ventral view with internal margins in contact on most of length and external margin slightly concave after process (fig. 
